   Marketing &amp; Media:
   Hachette S.A. Unit
   Is Planning Sale
   Of Woman's Day
   ----
   By Meg Cox
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
05/15/90
</DATE>
